Subject: Re: [plt-bug] all/10973: DrRacket Just Quits Early in Session
Date: Mon, 14 Jun 2010 12:50:28 -0500

 For point 3, you might just need to re-install the teaching (new
 versions require you to reinstall teachpacks, in general).
 
 And, to the larger concern: we do try as best we can to avoid
 incompatibilities, but it is not always possible, since we do make
 changes generally throughout the codebase. So, if I were you, I would
 let students use the latest version, but I would make a note somewhere
 about which version is known to work when you developed the examples,
 and keep that in mind as a fall back (since old versions are easy to
 install).
 
 Hope that helps.
 
 Robby
 
