   (lambda (n)
     (cond
       ((=3D n 0) 1)
       (else (* n (fact (sub1 n)))))))
 (map fact (build-list 10 identity))
 
 in DrRacket [5.0.2, MacOS X 10.6.5],
 I get
 
 Welcome to DrRacket, version 5.0.2 [3m].
